    • Method Detail

      • addItemSchema

        public ArraySchema.Builder addItemSchema​(Schema itemSchema)
        Adds an item schema for tuple validation. The array items of the subject under validation will be matched to expected schemas by their index. In other words the {n}th addItemSchema() invocation defines the expected schema of the {n}th item of the array being validated.
        Parameters:
        itemSchema - the schema of the next item.
        Returns:
        this
